Food Intake

Silvia Raineri

13/10/2020

Food Intake

Daily food (kJ) and water (g) intake were calculated for each animal. Food intake was calculated using the food energy values (20.79 kJ/g (high-fat chow), 23.44 kJ/g (chocolate) and 30.34 kJ/g (ground peanuts).

Combined food intake

Stats

Statistical significance was assessed by ANOVA with the model: value ~ Day + Treatment + Day*Treatment. P-values were corrected using the Benjamini-Hochberg method.
